                            "poster": "https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/res/images/playicon_wikiwijs.png"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\"><strong>Vraag: </strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Hoe werkt een windmolen? </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n"
